title: Episode 22 - The Rise of Indonesia 1945-49
itunes:author: The History of the Cold War Podcast
itunes:summary: Join us as we examine the the decline and fall of the Dutch East Indies and the Rise of Indonesia. How did small Holland come to rule a large island chain on the other side of the world ? Why did the Dutch East Indies fall and why didn't Communism spread to Indonesia like in Korea and Vietnam ?  Learn all this and more!
